《'''玩具總動員：夏威夷假期'''》（{{lang-en|''Toy Story Toons: Hawaiian Vacation''}}）是一部2011年由 [[皮克斯|皮克斯]]動畫導演[[加里·里德斯特罗姆|加里·里德斯特罗姆]]製作的動畫短片。本部片也是[[玩具總動員|玩具總動員]]系列的第一部短片，劇中的人物都是來自玩具總動員3的角色。這是一部收錄在[[汽車總動員2|汽車總動員2]]的影片。<ref name="MSN">{{cite news | url=http://movies.msn.com/the-rundown/toy-story-4/story_2/ | title=Closing Up the ''Toy'' Box? | accessdate=June 15, 2011 | last=Rocchi | first=James | publisher=''[[MSN|MSN]] Movies'' | archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5qt8skMym?url=http://movies.msn.com/the-rundown/toy-story-4/story_2/ | archivedate=2010-07-01 | dead-url=yes }}{{en}}</ref><ref name="Inside Movies">{{cite web | url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2011/03/01/toy-story-hawaiian-vacation-clip-reveals-return-of-the-toybox-gang-exclusive/ | title='Toy Story: Hawaiian Vacation' clip reveals return of the toybox gang – EXCLUSIVE | accessdate=March 5, 2011 | author=Breznican, Anthony | date=June 15, 2011 | work=Entertainment Weekly | archive-date=2012-05-22 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67q70j25S?url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2011/03/01/toy-story-hawaiian-vacation-clip-reveals-return-of-the-toybox-gang-exclusive/ | dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref><ref name= "CarpetBlogger">{{cite news|url=http://carpetbagger.blogs.nytimes.com/2011/02/17/the-toy-story-gang-to-ride-again/?src=mv|title=The 'Toy Story' Gang to Ride Again|work=The New York Times|date=February 17, 2011|accessdate=June 15, 2011|archive-date=2013-01-04|archive-url=https://archive.today/20130104074316/http://carpetbagger.blogs.nytimes.com/2011/02/17/the-toy-story-gang-to-ride-again/?src=mv|dead-url=yes}}{{en}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Weiner|first=David|title=ET Exclusive: 'Air Mater' Takes Flight|url=http://www.etonline.com/movies/113416_ET_Exclusive_Air_Mater_Takes_Flight_in_Cars_2_DVD/index.html|accessdate=August 18, 2011|newspaper=ET Online|date=August 18, 2011|archive-date=2011-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110920022056/http://www.etonline.com/movies/113416_ET_Exclusive_Air_Mater_Takes_F